name: GoPro HERO3+ Black Edition WiFi Enabled The most advanced GoPro yet.
description:
Features video resolutions up to 4K, 12MP photos up to 30 frames per second, built-in Wi-Fi, SuperView™ and Auto Low Light

Capture and share your life’s most meaningful experiences with the HERO3+ Black Edition. 20% smaller and lighter than its best-selling predecessor, it delivers improved image quality and powerful new features geared for versatility and convenience. SuperView™ is a new video mode that captures the world’s most immersive wide angle perspective, while Auto Low Light mode intelligently adjusts frame rate for stunning low-light performance. Combined with 30% longer battery life, 4x faster Wi-Fi, a sharper lens and compatibility with all GoPro mounts and accessories, the HERO3+ Black Edition is the most advanced GoPro yet.

The HERO3+ Black Edition is 20% smaller and lighter than previous models and is compatible with all GoPro mounts and accessories—making it the most mountable, wearable and versatile GoPro ever.

Stunning video quality has made GoPro the world’s best-selling camera company, and the HERO3+ Black Edition continues this tradition. High-resolution, high-frame rate 1440p48, 1080p60, 960p100 and 720p120 video modes result in professional quality footage and allow for liquid-smooth slow motion playback. 4Kp15 and 2.7Kp30 enable ultra high-resolution, cinema quality capture.

The HERO3+ Black Edition captures gorgeous 12MP stills at up to 30 frames per second—perfect for fast-action sequences. Time Lapse mode enables automatic photo capture at 0.5, 1, 2, 5, 10, 30 or 60 second intervals. Continuous Photo shoots full-resolution stills at a steady 3, 5 or 10 frames per second when holding down the shutter button.

GoPro is proud to introduce SuperView, a video mode that captures the world’s most immersive wide angle perspective. It allows you to capture more of yourself and your surroundings in the shot—resulting in captivating, ultra engaging footage.

Want your camera to automatically adjust for low-light situations? Auto Low Light mode intelligently changes frame rates based on lighting conditions for enhanced low-light performance.

Enjoy crisper, clearer footage with reduced distortion. The HERO3+ Black Edition boasts a 33% increase in image sharpness thanks to its sharper lens and 2x reduction in imaging artifacts.

Sound quality is as important as image quality. The HERO3+ Black Edition features upgraded audio performance, capturing even the most subtle of sounds—whether you’re recording voices, music or the roar of your engine on a spirited drive. Advanced wind-noise reduction technology keeps the audio clearer during high-speed activities.

Featuring a 30% increase in battery life, you can go longer and capture more with the HERO3+ Black Edition.

Speedier Wi-Fi delivers 4x faster2 video preview and faster photo and video sharing with the GoPro App than ever before. Also enjoy enhanced connectivity to the included Wi-Fi Remote, which enables control of up to 50 cameras from distances of up to 600’/180m.

name: Samurai British Army 'Letters Home' Poppy Rugby Shirt 2013
description:
This is the new British Army 'Letters Home' shirt for remembrance 2013. 

Standard fit, short sleeve design with standard collar. 

Design features a poppy field to the front and back with a soldiers letter home to the front and photographic soldier walking away image to the back with the poignant 'When you go home tell them of us and say for your tomorrow we gave our today' to the top of the shoulder area. 

The design is fully sublimated. 

A tribute to all those who have served our country.

name: ENGLAND HOME PRO RUGBY JERSEY WHITE
description:
The new England Home Rugby Pro short sleeved Jersey heralds the classic design of an "all-white" traditional England jersey allowing the iconic red rose emblem to take centre stage contrasting against the white. 

This New England Jersey is tailored to fit a range of body shapes and features the revolutionary 'Loop 2.3' neckline, adding strength and reducing the chances of tears with internal triple bartacks and power Lycra binding. 

The neckline also features 'Roses' hooped neckline tape and the St George's cross on the reverse.

name: Canterbury England Alternative Replica Rugby Shirt Biking Red
description:
The new England Alternate Rugby Pro Jersey offers a stylish twist on the traditional home jersey. 

This striking Biking red hoops on an Ecru body reflects the heritage of the game. Adorning the front of the chest is an embroidered twill applique shield heritage logo, CCC featuring on the right shoulder and sublimated sponsorship logo across the central panel. 

A fitted design, the Alternate Pro shirt features the revolutionising signature 'Loop 2.3' neckline, adding strength and reducing the chances of tears with internal triple bartacks and power lycra binding.  

On the reserve of the England Alternate rugby pro shirt features a heritage style number patch and the St Georges cross on the collar heralding the memories of traditional rugby shirts.

description:

The quilted gilet is an essential layer with a high collar for further protection from the elements encompassing the vivid blue lining. 

Adorning the front of the England Gilet are embroidered logos with the Iconic red rose featuring on the left chest, CCC logo on the right and a sponsor logo on the top of the zip.  

The England gilet also has two zip pockets on the front, a woven tag featuring on the side seam and logo on the reverse hem.

name: Cornwall Select 15 / Clubs XV Mens Rugby Shirt Black/Gold
description:
CORNWALL
SELECT XV
RUGBY SHIRT
2013

This is the Cornwall Clubs Select XV that will be worn at the Festival of Rugby August 30th 2013 against the Cornish Pirates.

This Black shirt with Gold accents has each of the Cornwall Clubs names sublimated into the shirt in the shape of Cornwall, the front of the shirt also features a silhouette of a Cornish Tin mine.

The back of the shirt features a St.Pirans flag draped down the back with a number 15 on each and every replica shirt to signify the 'Select XV'. The back of this shirt is topped off with 'One And All' sublimated at the bottom.

The shirt is flanked with a St.Pirans flag on each arm.

This shirt is truly a one off and was designed in Cornwall by a Cornishman, it will not be repeated so this is your only chance to own a bit of Cornish Rugby history.
